---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import headshotImage from '../assets/images/rudy-headshot.jpg';
---

<Layout
  title="About Rudy Corona | Corona Lending Group"
  description="Meet Rudy Corona, your trusted California modern mortgage advisor. Licensed, experienced, and committed to getting you the best loan."
  pathname="/about"
>
  <section class="bg-navy text-white py-16 md:py-24 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
      <div>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Meet Rudy Corona — Your California Modern Mortgage Advisor</h1>
        <p class="text-white/90 text-lg mb-8">
          I believe everyone deserves expert guidance on the biggest financial decision of their life.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block min-h-[44px] px-8 py-4 bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105">
          Book a Call
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-end">
        <img src={headshotImage.src} alt="Rudy Corona" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-md aspect-square object-cover" width="400" height="400" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">Rudy's Story</h2>
      <p class="text-dark/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        I got into mortgages because I saw too many families confused and underserved by big banks and faceless online lenders. I wanted to be the advisor I'd want for my own family—someone who explains every option, shops the market, and fights for the best deal.
      </p>
      <p class="text-dark/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        I work with first-time buyers taking the leap into homeownership, seniors exploring reverse mortgages and retirement planning, and investors building their portfolios. Whatever stage you're in, I'm here to guide you with transparency, speed, and a commitment to your success.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-sky-light">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">Credentials & Experience</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-dark/90">
        <li><strong>NMLS License #</strong> 999113</li>
        <li>Licensed in California</li>
        <li>15+ years in the mortgage industry</li>
        <li>Access to 50+ lenders and programs</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">Values & Mission</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-dark/90">
        <li><strong class="text-navy">Transparency</strong> — No hidden fees or confusing jargon. You'll always know where you stand.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-navy">Speed</strong> — Efficient process that respects your time. We close loans in as few as 21 days when possible.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-navy">Community</strong> — Proudly serving California families. Your success is my success.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-navy text-white text-center">
    <p class="text-xl mb-6">Let's get started. Your free consultation is one click away.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="inline-block min-h-[44px] px-8 py-4 bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105">
      Book Now
    </a>
  </section>
</Layout>
